---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AG composition">
  <p class="text-sm text-ink-subtle"><a href="/managers">← Managers</a></p>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-6">AG composition</h1>

  <p class="text-ink-muted max-w-2xl">
    The Advisory Group (ISO 24229/AG) consists of at least 4 and up to 12
    experts in script or other conversions, information technologies, and
    library management. The AG includes a representative of ISO/TC 46 and
    may include representatives of organizations that use the codes.
    Members are appointed by the Registration Authority.
  </p>

  <p class="mt-8 text-ink-muted">
    The current member roster will be published here once finalised by the Registration Authority.
  </p>
</Layout>
